data.description: Property is located across the street from the Rogue River, one mile from Hog Creek, just past the famous Robertson Bridge! Home is a two-story, with a man cave located in the day-lite basement. Large living room with three bedrooms and two full baths on main level. Laminate floors thru out with four separate doors leading to the outside wooded setting. Towering Pines give this property a secluded feel as you follow the circular driveway. There is a detached two car garage, a one car garage attached to home, plus two large shops on the property. Perfect for an in home business. Come take a look!!
